    "Harvard Professor of Fine Arts and Director of the Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, 1935-1954.": [],
    "Edgell was the son of George Stephen Edgell (d.": [],
    "1915), a banker, whose New England lineage traced back to 1636.": [],
    "His mother was Isabella Wallace Corbin (Edgell).": [],
    "Edgell entered Harvard University, receiving his B.A.": [],
