    "Edgell received an honorary doctorate from Harvard in 1948.": [],
    "The following year he published his <em>History of Sienese Painting</em>.": [],
    "He died unexpectedly at his summer home in New Hampshire after a brief illness and was succeeded by <a href=\"/rathbonep\">Perry T. Rathbone</a>.": [],
    "His papers are held at Harvard.": [],
    "Students whose dissertation he supervised may have included <a href=\"/smithr\">Robert C. Smith</a>.": [],
    "In his memoirs, <a href=\"/wittmanno\">Otto Wittmann, Jr.</a>, described Edgell as a brilliant lecturer.": []
